premise_source_doc_sentence: Morgan Freeman  (  born June 1 , 1937  )  is an American actor , producer and narrator .

Freeman won an Academy Award in 2005 for Best Supporting Actor with Million Dollar Baby  (  2004  )  , and he has received Oscar nominations for his performances in Street Smart  (  1987  )  , Driving Miss Daisy  (  1989  )  , The Shawshank Redemption  (  1994  )  and Invictus  (  2009  )  .
He has also won a Golden Globe Award and a Screen Actors Guild Award .

Freeman has appeared in many other box office hits , including Glory  (  1989  )  , Robin Hood : Prince of Thieves  (  1991  )  , Seven  (  1995  )  , Deep Impact  (  1998  )  , The Sum of All Fears  (  2002  )  , Bruce Almighty  (  2003  )  , The Dark Knight Trilogy  (  2005 -- 2012  )  , The Lego Movie  (  2014  )  , and Lucy  (  2014  )  .
He rose to fame as part of the cast of the 1970s children 's program The Electric Company .
